    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "ing a routine patrol for the North Da-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "kota National Guard, and had called",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "the tower at the Fargo Municipal Air-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "port for clearance to land when he saw",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "what seemed to be another plane's tail-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "light a thousand yards away. He queried",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "the tower, and the men there reported",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "that the only other aircraft over the field",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "was a Piper Cub. Gorman could see the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "Cub plainly outlined below him. Curi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "ous, he flew toward the light. \"It was",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "about six to eight inches in diameter,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "clear white, and completely round, with",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "a sort of fuzz at the edges,\" Gorman",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "later told investigators, adding that he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "saw \"no outline of anything\" around",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "the edges. \"It was blinking on and off.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "As I approached, however, the light sud-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "denly became steady and pulled into",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "a sharp left bank. . . . I dived after it",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "and brought my manifold pressure up",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "to sixty inches, but I couldn't catch up",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "with the thing. It started gaining alti-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "tude and again made a left bank. I put",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "my F-51 into a sharp turn and tried",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "to cut the light off in its turn. By then,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "we were at about seven thousand feet.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "Suddenly it made a sharp right turn",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 71,
      "text": "and we headed straight at each other.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 72,
      "text": "Just when we were about to collide,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 73,
      "text": "I guess I got scared. I went into a dive",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 74,
      "text": "and the light passed over my canopy at",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 75,
      "text": "about five hundred feet. Then it made",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 76,
      "text": "a left circle about a thousand feet above,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 77,
      "text": "and I gave chase again.\" Gorman fol-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 78,
      "text": "lowed the light up to fourteen thousand",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 79,
      "text": "feet, where, after another near collision,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 80,
      "text": "his ship went into a power stall and the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 81,
      "text": "light disappeared to the northwest.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 82,
      "text": "Gorman noticed no sounds or exhaust-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 83,
      "text": "trail odors. He had gunned his plane",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 84,
      "text": "up to four hundred miles an hour with-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 85,
      "text": "out gaining on the light. It was able to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 86,
      "text": "maintain an extremely steep angle of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 87,
      "text": "ascent, far greater than that of his Air",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 88,
      "text": "Force fighter. \"When I attempted to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 89,
      "text": "turn with [the light], I blacked out",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 90,
      "text": "temporarily, due to excessive speed,\" he",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 91,
      "text": "said. \"I am in fairly good physical condi-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 92,
      "text": "tion and I do not believe there are many,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 93,
      "text": "if any, pilots who could withstand the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 94,
      "text": "turn and speed effected by that light and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 95,
      "text": "remain conscious.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 96,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 97,
      "text": "Project Saucer suspected that Gor-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 98,
      "text": "man was tilting with a weather balloon.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 99,
      "text": "For one thing, it learned that the Fargo",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 100,
      "text": "weather station had released a lighted",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 101,
      "text": "balloon only ten minutes before Gor-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 102,
      "text": "man's patrol stopped being routine.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 103,
      "text": "The object's steady, practically vertical",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 104,
      "text": "climb suggested the behavior of a bal-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 105,
      "text": "loon. A technician who once worked on",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 106,
      "text": "Project Saucer told me recently that",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 107,
      "text": "chasing a weather balloon with an air-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 108,
      "text": "plane is comparable to diving to the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 109,
      "text": "bottom of a pool after a hollow rubber",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 110,
      "status": "blank"
    },
